data.description:
Discover spacious living in the heart of O'Fallon! This all-brick ranch on a generous corner lot seamlessly blends comfort w/convenience. The welcoming foyer introduces a bright & open living/dining area, bathed in beautiful natural light. The updated eat-in kitchen boasts granite countertops & nearly new (2023) appliances, offering style & functionality w/abundant cabinet space.
A wood burning, tile fireplace serves as a stunning focal point, providing warmth on chilly days. Built-in shelves accentuate the room, adding storage for games, puzzles or books & transforming the family room into a haven for gatherings. Three generously sized bedrooms, including a primary ensuite w/walk-in closet, ensure comfort & relaxation. Newer faux wood blinds enhance the home, providing a touch of modern elegance. Main floor laundry, fenced yard, sideload garage, patio, & storage shed, complete the highlights of this residence. O'Fallon schools. Minutes to hospitals, SAFB, interstates and shopping.
